== Description ==

The '''BIM Nudge''' tools are a set of tools that move, rotate, or change the height of selected objects. For the rotation a fixed value of 45° is used. The other operations use a nudge distance. The nudge distance can be set to a fixed value or to ''Auto'' mode, which automatically scales the nudge distance based on the current view zoom level.

